      "raw": "{\"prompt\":\"Create a 3×3 grid poster for Xiaohongshu (Little Red Book) — a 9-panel layout designed for slicing into 9 individual posts.\\n\\nStyle/medium: needs a clean, premium, \\\"小红书爆款\\\" aesthetic — exact stylistic restraint is yours\\nComposition: must be 3 columns × 3 rows grid layout with clear boundaries between panels, each panel centered and complete, no text near split lines, obvious spacing or thin borders for clean cropping\\nSubject: must include sleep/relaxation themed elements across panels: soft bed, moon, pillow, eye mask, warm lamp, curtains, hot milk, aromatherapy, books, AC, thermometer, coffee cup, bathtub steam, notebook, pen, clock, breathing visualization lines\\nScene/backdrop: must be cream-white, light beige, pale oatmeal, soft caramel color palette with minimal deep brown text accents — exact color values are yours\\nLighting/mood: needs a gentle, healing, sleep-therapy atmosphere — exact light source mix is yours\\nColor palette: must be warm cream, beige, oatmeal, caramel tones with deep brown text\\nMaterials/textures: needs a soft, tactile, light skeuomorphic illustration style — exact material treatment is yours\\nText (verbatim): must include all Chinese text across 9 panels:\\n  Panel 1 (cover): \\\"让你倒头就睡的8个 tips\\\" (large title), \\\"失眠党、熬夜党一定要收藏\\\" (subtitle)\\n  Panel 2: \\\"1. 睡前1小时别玩手机\\\" (title), \\\"蓝光会让大脑更清醒，越刷越睡不着。\\\" (body)\\n  Panel 3: \\\"2. 睡前把灯光调暗\\\" (title), \\\"暖光环境能帮助身体进入\\\"准备睡觉\\\"的状态。\\\" (body)\\n  Panel 4: \\\"3. 房间温度别太高\\\" (title), \\\"稍微凉一点，更容易快速入睡。\\\" (body)\\n  Panel 5: \\\"4. 晚上别喝浓茶咖啡\\\" (title), \\\"咖啡因会延迟困意，让你躺很久还睡不着。\\\" (body)\\n  Panel 6: \\\"5. 睡前洗个热水澡\\\" (title), \\\"能让身体放松下来，入睡速度更快。\\\" (body)\\n  Panel 7: \\\"6. 脑子停不下来就写下来\\\" (title), \\\"把烦心事和待办清单写下，大脑会更容易放松。\\\" (body)\\n  Panel 8: \\\"7. 固定上床时间\\\" (title), \\\"每天差不多时间睡，生物钟会越来越稳定。\\\" (body)\\n  Panel 9: \\\"8. 试试深呼吸放松法\\\" (title), \\\"吸气4秒，停4秒，呼气6秒，慢慢就有困意了。\\\" (body), \\\"收藏这组，今晚试试看\\\" (footer)\\nConstraints: must be 3:4 vertical aspect ratio, all 9 panels must function as standalone Xiaohongshu cards when cropped, consistent visual style across all panels, magazine-quality layout, readable large text, comfortable white space, no cheap marketing feel, no excessive decoration, all text in Chinese only, no English\\nAvoid: must avoid cheap marketing aesthetics, excessive ornamentation, text too close to grid lines, garbled characters, English text\",\"size\":\"1152x1536\",\"quality\":\"medium\",\"n\":1,\"output_format\":\"png\"}",
