      "final_prompt": {
        "prompt": "Create a 3:4 vertical 3×3 grid poster for Xiaohongshu (Little Red Book) lifestyle content.\n\nStyle/medium: needs a \"干净、高级、治愈感\" aesthetic with \"ins风\" and \"小红书爆款封面\" direction — references in the spirit of 2010s Instagram lifestyle flatlay photography, Muji minimalist editorial design, Korean wellness brand visual identity (e.g., Aesop, Innisfree); exact stylistic execution is yours\nComposition: must be standard 3×3 grid layout (3 columns × 3 rows), each cell complete and centered, clear boundaries between cells for clean slicing, all text in Chinese, generous whitespace, magazine-quality typography\nSubject: must include 9 grid cells with sleep wellness content:\n  Cell 1 (cover): 大标题\"让你倒头就睡的8个 tips\" + 副标题\"失眠党、熬夜党一定要收藏\" + 柔软床铺、月亮、枕头、眼罩等治愈睡眠元素\n  Cell 2: 标题\"1. 睡前1小时别玩手机\" + 正文\"蓝光会让大脑更清醒，越刷越睡不着。\" + 手机、月亮、困倦表情插画\n  Cell 3: 标题\"2. 睡前把灯光调暗\" + 正文\"暖光环境能帮助身体进入\"准备睡觉\"的状态。\" + 床头灯、暖黄色灯光、窗帘\n  Cell 4: 标题\"3. 房间温度别太高\" + 正文\"稍微凉一点，更容易快速入睡。\" + 空调、温度计、被子\n  Cell 5: 标题\"4. 晚上别喝浓茶咖啡\" + 正文\"咖啡因会延迟困意，让你躺很久还睡不着。\" + 咖啡杯、茶杯、禁止符号\n  Cell 6: 标题\"5. 睡前洗个热水澡\" + 正文\"能让身体放松下来，入睡速度更快。\" + 浴室蒸汽、毛巾、热水\n  Cell 7: 标题\"6. 脑子停不下来就写下来\" + 正文\"把烦心事和待办清单写下，大脑会更容易放松。\" + 笔记本、钢笔、小台灯\n  Cell 8: 标题\"7. 固定上床时间\" + 正文\"每天差不多时间睡，生物钟会越来越稳定。\" + 时钟、月亮、床\n  Cell 9: 标题\"8. 试试深呼吸放松法\" + 正文\"吸气4秒，停4秒，呼气6秒，慢慢就有困意了。\" + 底部小字\"收藏这组，今晚试试看\" + 呼吸线条、闭眼人物、星星\nScene/backdrop: must be unified cream/beige/oatmeal background throughout all 9 cells\nLighting/mood: needs a \"温柔治愈\" atmosphere — exact light source mix is yours\nColor palette: must be cream white, light beige, pale oatmeal, light caramel dominant with dark brown text accents — exact hex values are yours\nMaterials/textures: needs a \"轻拟物插画\" surface treatment with soft illustrations — exact illustration style is yours\nText (verbatim): must include all Chinese text as specified in each cell above\nConstraints: must preserve 3×3 grid structure for clean slicing into 9 individual posts, each cell must work as standalone image,