      "raw": "{\"prompt\":\"Create a 9:16 vertical screenshot of a Douyin livestream featuring \\\"神仙姐姐\\\" (Fairy Sister).\\n\\nStyle/medium: needs a livestream UI aesthetic — references in the spirit of Douyin/TikTok interface design language, Chinese influencer livestream visual culture, 2020s mobile streaming app interfaces; exact stylistic execution is yours\\nComposition: must be 9:16 vertical frame with livestream interface elements (comments, likes, gift buttons visible)\\nSubject: must include \\\"神仙姐姐\\\" as the streamer, holding a sign\\nScene/backdrop: must be a livestream room setting with typical Douyin UI overlay\\nLighting/mood: needs a warm, engaging livestream atmosphere — exact light source mix is yours\\nColor palette: needs a vibrant livestream direction — exact hex values are yours\\nMaterials/textures: \\nText (verbatim): must include \\\"今晚直播，欢迎来参亦菲畅聊！\\\" on the sign\\nConstraints: must preserve 9:16 aspect ratio, livestream UI elements visible, sign clearly readable\\nAvoid: \",\"size\":\"1008x1792\",\"quality\":\"medium\",\"n\":1,\"output_format\":\"png\"}",
