el, e-commerce layout, anime illustration, cosplay aesthetics, messy labeling, incorrect structure, blurry text, fake materials, excessive decoration\",\"size\":\"1536x1024\",\"quality\":\"medium\",\"n\":1,\"output_format\":\"png\"}",
